{
  "stem": "734.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Things would spill and people would get totally, I mean, degraded and-- and-- and disgusted about this whole thing.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And everybody was ready to give up, really.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And he kept preaching about how to keep healthy, how to keep clean, and all that.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And suddenly this man who was a Warsaw ghetto fighter, Schlomo, he probably overreacted a bit.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "He came over to him and he gave him an argument.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And to make a long story short-- --this German fellow says to him, look, if you don't think I'm doing anything right, he said, you take over.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Now, let me see what you can do.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Well, they had this argument.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And eventually he-- [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] The train stopped.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I think the train stopped because somebody escaped, I think it was the same train.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I'm not sure any longer, whether this was the transport or not.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "I get so mixed up with these transports, from where to where.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Uh-- at some point, the train stopped and they pulled off-- They pulled them off.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "We had to get-- we had to get out of the train.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Because they wanted to count us to see whether anybody escaped from our car.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And of course, nobody from our car did escape.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "But there were other-- there were some other people who escaped from a different car.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "They had partly lifted boards from the floor.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And they were able-- at the-- when the train was making a-- a turn, a curve, at the sharp curve, apparently some people were able to lower them-- themselves out of the car and escape.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And of course, they shot them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "Because the guards on the roof noticed.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
